## arrays.ArrayContains class

Matches an Array which contains elements that match the given matchers - note that two different matchers may be satisfied by the same item in the array.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare class ArrayContains extends AnyMatcher
```

**Extends:** [AnyMatcher](./test-equivalence-matchers.base.anymatcher.md)
